What about Jan? Lovely, lovely, lovely Jan, man. It's goin' good, right?
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                      I couldn't do it. I--- I ain't that strong. And I ain't that brave.
